# =============================================================================
# MAIL MODULE SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================
# 
# 1. SUPABASE SETUP:
#    - Create a new Supabase project
#    - Run the database migration: database/migrations/20250113_mail_module_setup.sql
#    - Get your project URL and keys from Settings > API
#
# 2. UPSTASH SETUP:
#    - Create Redis database at https://console.upstash.com/redis
#    - Create QStash account at https://console.upstash.com/qstash
#    - Get your tokens from the dashboard
#
# 3. ZEPTOMAIL SETUP:
#    - Sign up at https://www.zoho.com/zeptomail/
#    - Get your API key from Settings > API
#    - Set up webhook endpoint: https://your-domain.com/api/mail/webhooks/zeptomail
#
# 4. STRIPE SETUP:
#    - Create Stripe account at https://stripe.com
#    - Get your API keys from Developers > API keys
#    - Create products and prices for email plans
#    - Set up webhook endpoint: https://your-domain.com/api/mail/webhooks/stripe
#
# 5. CLOUDFLARE SETUP (optional):
#    - Get API token from Cloudflare dashboard
#    - Token needs Zone:Edit permissions
#
# 6. ENCRYPTION KEY:
#    - Generate a random 32-character string
#    - Use: openssl rand -base64 32
